# year		year of the growing season
# harvest_date		date of harvest or G11 sampling
# dry_matter_yield_mg_ha	megagramsPerHectare	yield as dry matter
# moisture_at_harvest	gramsPerHectogram	percent moisture measured at harvest
# comments		specific notes for a given row

#2014 yield calculations- Wisconsin removed the area of the ANPP sampling (3- 1m2 quadrats/plot).  Michigan did not remove the ANPP sampling area because the ANPP may not have been in the harvested area and this area was it was very minor.

column2: 2016- Michigan 2014 yield calculations and Michigan and Wisconsin 2015 G11 yield were corrected.
